Usage: saveColorPreference [-help] [-dir <string>] [-include_customized]
                           -name <string>

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-dir <string>           # Specify the directorpath, default is current folder
                        # (string, optional)
-include_customized     # Include Customize Tab Setting (bool, optional)
-name <string>          # Specify the saved filename (string, required)